      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2026-02",
        "text": "Where do I start my glowing review for Sunbeam Studio. First, April, the owner, is incredibly talented, along with just about every stylist in the salon. My current stylist, Kenzie, is unfortunately moving, but I don’t hesitate to switch as I know every stylist here is gifted.\n\nThey crush blonde highlights, excel at gray grow out (I am in this category), extensions, cuts, and so much more. April has put so much intention into the decor, experience, vibe, clean product selection, and green practices. My hair always looks amazing after a visit. Another bonus is the salon chargers per hour vs per service. So, if you need a toner, a gloss can be done simultaneously without an extra treatment charge, bonus!! Spending 2+ hours here is no problem with all the amenities and comforts (drinks, snacks, etc).\n\nI could not recommend this salon more highly. Find out for yourself!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2026-06",
        "text": "Lovely salon with even lovelier people. Anna is truly an artist and a joy to spend time with. Her results in both cut and color are consistently stunning and natural looking.  I have Pinterest worthy hair and that still looks great after several months because her root blending grows out seamlessly."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-12",
        "text": "Sierra at Sunbeam is THE BEST! After moving to Colorado, I was having such a hard time finding a stylist that not only understands what I am asking for, but is actually able to get there. After 2 appointments with other stylists in Denver, I finally was recommended to Sierra. From day 1, I have been so happy with my hair color and extensions! I feel like a bestie in her chair, and Sunbeam is the cutest, most welcoming salon! Even after moving to Lakewood, I still drive almost an hour every 6 weeks to see Sierra. (Short hair photos BEFORE Sierra, long hair is color and extensions by Sierra)"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-12",
        "text": "After many years with the same stylist that was a long drive I switched to Sunbeam. I’ve seen several of the stylists here and had great experiences with each. Everyone here listens closely to what you want and results are natural and long lasting. Techniques are gentle on your hair and have helped with my hair health. There are always ongoing improvements to the salon itself, which is such a calm and relaxing environment."
      },
